Package: pdl
Type: Package
Title: Polynomial Distributed-Lag Models
Version: 0.0
Date: 2021-04-01
Author: Federica Sauro Graziano
Maintainer: Federica Sauro Graziano <federica.sauro@stud.unifi.it>
Description: Estimation of polynomial distributed-lag models. Currently, the general polynomial lag by Almon (1965) is available, together with two constrained polynomial lags: (i) linearly decreasing, and (ii) parabolic with endpoint constraints.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0), ggplot2
Imports: graphics, stats
License: GPL-2
NeedsCompilation: no
